    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were not assessed and represent epistemic gaps. The literature review of published hemolysis correlations was judged to provide sufficient supporting evidence that the CFD model captures the correct order of magnitude for hemolysis index across the VAD operating envelope. The team concluded that, taken together with Monte Carlo UQ results, the model is adequate for the intended use. Decision: Accepted.",
